    <div class="czr-stage w-reveal" aria-label="Customer reviews"><div class="czr-side czr-side--lo"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Every renewal now opens with a customer who’s been exactly where this account is. That moves more than any deck we ever built.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-33.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>Allison Moore</b><small>Head of CS</small></div><span class="czr-metric">+21% retention</span></div></div></div><div class="czr-side czr-side--lm"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Carly identifies the story each deal needs and gets it in front of the buyer before we’d have thought to ask. Replies doubled.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-34.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>Aisha Bell</b><small>VP Sales</small></div><span class="czr-metric">2× reply rate</span></div></div></div><div class="czr-side czr-side--li"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Reference calls that took a week of chasing now book in hours, with zero rep effort. Our deals move at a different speed.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-35.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>George Stevens</b><small>RevOps Lead</small></div><span class="czr-metric">5 days → hours</span></div></div></div><figure class="czr-main"><svg class="czr-qi czr-qi--lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><blockquote class="czr-q czr-q--lg">We completely rethought our demo follow-up process. Now prospects can instantly connect with customers who’ve solved similar challenges. It’s accelerated our entire sales motion.</blockquote><figcaption class="czr-by"><span class="czr-av czr-av--bg" style="background-image:var(--w-img-av-keegan)"></span><div class="czr-meta"><b>Keegan Otter</b><small>Head of Revenue · Warmly</small></div><span class="czr-metric czr-metric--on">25% shorter cycle</span></figcaption></figure><div class="czr-side czr-side--ri"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Buyers believe peers, not pitches. Carly puts the right proof in front of every buyer at the moment it counts. Win rate up 38% in a quarter.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-36.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>Joseph White</b><small>Sales Director</small></div><span class="czr-metric">+38% win rate</span></div></div></div><div class="czr-side czr-side--rm"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Proof reaches every open deal now — not just the ones someone remembered. Nothing we’ve earned sits unused.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-37.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>Ava Cheng</b><small>CMO</small></div><span class="czr-metric">3× proof sent</span></div></div></div><div class="czr-side czr-side--ro"><div class="czr-card"><svg class="czr-qi" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#i-quote"/></svg><p class="czr-q">Our best customers quietly became our best pipeline source, with no referral program required. Carly turned goodwill into tracked demand.</p><div class="czr-by"><img class="czr-av" src="/assets/images/w/carly/asset-38.webp" alt=""><div class="czr-meta"><b>Amy Lee</b><small>Demand Gen</small></div><span class="czr-metric">4× referrals</span></div></div></div></div>
